Scene 1 (Anchor Scene) Prompt:

Create a vibrant children's storybook illustration for this scene:

SCENE DESCRIPTION:
ocean shore at sunset, Lalli (caring 6yo girl with curly brown hair), Fafa (silly 3yo boy with bright blue shirt), and Priya (brave 7yo girl with long black hair), excitedly searching for shells, warm-happy-excited mood, golden sky with soft pink clouds and gentle waves

Include the characters Lalli and Fafa exactly as they appear in the 'Reference image of Lalli and Fafa'.
Also include the child character. Use the 'Reference image for the child character's appearance' to draw Priya.

Art Style: bright, clean, warm cartoon style, consistent with all reference images.
Composition: engaging and centered, child-friendly lighting, colorful background.


